---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="lastGLANCE"
  description="lastGLANCE is a calm tracker for the recurring upkeep in your life. Cleaning, car maintenance, pet care, health care, finances."
  ogImage="/og/lastglance.svg"
>
  <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="mb-10 font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-glance-muted transition-colors">GLANCE Apps</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-glance-muted">lastGLANCE</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left column -->
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold leading-none mb-4">
          <span class="text-glance-muted font-medium">last</span><span style="color: #3DDB84;" class="tracking-wider font-bold">GLANCE</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-glance-muted font-serif italic mb-8">
          When did you last...?
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-glance-muted font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <p>
            lastGLANCE is a calm tracker for the recurring upkeep in your life.
            Cleaning, car maintenance, pet care, health care, finances. The things
            you don't want to forget but don't want to nag you. Built with the same
            care as the rest of the GLANCE family.
          </p>
          <p>
            No streaks to break. No nagging notifications. Just an honest record
            of when you last did the things that matter, so you can decide what
            needs your attention.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Platforms -->
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-3">
            Platforms
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted mb-1">Web</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim">Android · macOS · Windows · Linux · iOS (all coming soon)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6">
          <a
            href="/apps/lastglance/downloads"
            class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted hover:text-glance-accent transition-colors duration-150"
            style="color: #3DDB84;"
          >
            All downloads →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- What it does -->
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-5">
            What it does
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-3">Core</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted mb-5">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #3DDB84;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Last-done tracking</strong>: Track when you last did something. See everything at a glance, color-coded by how long it's been. Drill in for per-item history, custom completion dates, and notes.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #3DDB84;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Flexible organization</strong>: Group items into categories and subcategories. Make a category per pet, per room, per car. Whatever fits your life.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #3DDB84;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">One-tap done</strong>: Mark something done with a single click. No forms, no friction. The card returns to fresh and the timer resets.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #3DDB84;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Activity heatmap</strong>: A visual history of when you actually did things, across everything you track.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="border-t border-glance-border pt-5">
            <p class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-3">Optional</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted leading-relaxed">
              Cadence targets and reminders for things you don't want to forget. All off by default.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cloud Sync -->
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
            Cloud Sync
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted leading-relaxed">
            Optional sync across your devices. No GLANCE Apps account. No GLANCE Apps servers. Zero-knowledge encrypted to a destination you control. Off by default.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-10 section-rule">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
        Open Source
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        lastGLANCE is open source under the MIT License. Self-host the web app,
        build from source, or audit the code. Purchases on the app stores support
        continued development.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/krelltunez/lastGLANCE"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-sans last-accent-link link-underline"
      >
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="shrink-0 opacity-75">
          <path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        View on GitHub →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-10 section-rule">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
        Privacy
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        lastGLANCE stores your data locally on your device. No account required.
        No data leaves your device without your direction. Your data remains yours.
      </p>
      <a href="/privacy" class="font-sans text-sm last-accent-link link-underline">
        Privacy policy →
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .last-accent-link {
    color: #3DDB84;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: #3DDB8440;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.15s, text-decoration-color 0.15s;
  }
  .last-accent-link:hover {
    text-decoration-color: #3DDB84;
  }
</style>
